        <p style="max-width: 600px; font-size: 1.1rem;">Architecting high-performance cross-platform applications with a focus on scalable code and fluid UI/UX.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card stats">
        <div class="stat-item"><h3>4+</h3><p>Years XP</p></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><h3>15+</h3><p>Apps Live</p></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><h3>60</h3><p>FPS Fluid</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card social">
        <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i> LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-github"></i> GitHub</a>
        <a href="mailto:swarajya888@gmail.com" class="social-link" style="background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 800;">HIRE ME</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card experience">
        <h2>Professional Journey</h2>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 30px; position: relative; padding-left: 20px; border-left: 2px solid var(--border);">
            <h4 style="color: white;">Full Stack Freelancer</h4>
            <small style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">2025 — Present</small>
            <ul>
                <li>Leading "Kharcha" - A premium finance app with Bento UI.</li>
                <li>Full-stack systems using Node.js & PostgreSQL.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="position: relative; padding-left: 20px; border-left: 2px solid var(--border);">
            <h4 style="color: white;">Senior Flutter Developer</h4>
            <small style="color: var(--text-dim);">Sunra Softtech | 2022 — 2025</small>
            <ul>
                <li>Developed Sense Wheel OTT with offline encryption.</li>
                <li>Optimized legacy architectures for high-traffic apps.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card projects">
        <h2>Selected Works</h2>
        <div class="project-item">
            <h4 style="color: white;">Jeeyo Ride</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Real-time cab booking engine utilizing Socket.io for live tracking and seamless driver-user handshake.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-item">
            <h4 style="color: white;">Sense Wheel</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">High-end OTT platform featuring PodPlayer integration and secure, encrypted offline storage protocols.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>